caption:
Our last 5 minute meditation was created to support you during a night shift. It can be a challenging time to stay focused, but no matter the time of day, people need care.

When things get tough, we often need a bit of help and a reminder to recenter and reconnect with ourselves. 5 minutes of downtime is sometimes all it takes to cultivate a clear and focused mind.

Find the full meditation in our story highlights.
